kpi_info.title: TRANSFERRED DATA FOR PS RT DCH UL
kpi_info.use: The amount of MAC-d PDU data transferred in RT PS DCH in uplink direction during measurement interval. The counter is updated at 20 second intervals or when the connection is released or when active set is changed.
